**> 制約条件の設定
param(max-seconds, 1)
param(max-given, 50)
param(inv-check-max-depth, 4)

flag(quiet,on)
flag(print-proofs,off)
flag(print-stats,on)
**

open PROOF
db reset

**> SOS の設定
sos = { SOS SOS1 }

